    "description": "Plans geometric serial dilution series for molecular biology and biochemistry workflows, rounding transfer volumes to declared pipette ranges and optional 96- or 384-well plate layouts. A browser calculator supports interactive protocol design; a Python client and command-line tool submit the same parameters to the Pepkio Tools API for scripted and pipeline use. Calculator arithmetic is hosted remotely; the client transmits parameters and returns structured step tables and shareable run identifiers.",
